  i Not clearing the observer can cause memory leaks and trigger duplicate observations on an unmounted component.
  
  i Return a cleanup function from the effect that calls disconnect on the observer object.
  
  i This rule belongs to the nursery group, which means it is not yet stable and may change in the future. Visit https://biomejs.dev/linter/#nursery for more information.
  

